title: Uber Backend (SpringBoot)
description: I created a ride-hailing system like Uber with five entities: Admin, Customer, Driver, Cab, and TripBooking. The system offers dependable and efficient service while preserving the privacy of customer and driver data. It allows customers to book and cancel trips, assigns drivers and cabs, updates cab status, and stores trip information.
